    ],
    "text": "PART!",
    "fonts": [
      "*Minion Pro-10283"
    ],
    "sizes": [
      10.5
    ]
  },
  {
    "page_number": 1,
    "bbox": [
      91.91,
      289.06,
      287.96,
      298.47
    ],
    "text": "COMMERCIAL MEDIATION CENTRE OF SRI LANKA",
    "fonts": [
      "*Cambria-10281"
    ],
    "sizes": [
      7.0
    ]
  },
  {
    "page_number": 1,
    "bbox": [
      67.66,
      309.21,
      312.73,
      343.76
    ],
    "text": "2.(I) There shall be established a Centre to be calledthe Commercial Mediation Centre of Sri Lanka (hereinafter referred to as \"the Centre\").",
    "fonts": [
      "*Minion Pro-10283"
    ],
    "sizes": [
      10.5
    ]
  },
  {
    "page_number": 1,
    "bbox": [
      67.59,
      353.37,
      312.55,
      400.14
    ],
    "text": "(2) The Centre shall. by the name assigned to it bysubsection ( I), be a body corporate with perpetual succession and a common seal, and may sue and be sued in it's corporate name.",
    "fonts": [
      "*Minion Pro-10283"
    ],
    "sizes": [
      10.5
    ]
  },
  {
    "page_number": 1,
    "bbox": [
      67.78,
      409.7,
      313.1,
      456.4
    ],
    "text": "(3) The head office of the Centre shall be in Colombo. TheBoard of Management of the Centre may establish such branch offices of the Centre as the Board may consider necesssary in places in Sri Lanka, outside Colombo.",
    "fonts": [
      "*Minion Pro-10283"
    ],
    "sizes": [
      10.5
    ]
  },
  {
    "page_number": 1,
    "bbox": [
      80.37,
      467.16,
      250.99,
      477.84
    ],
    "text": "3.The functions of the Centre shall be -",
    "fonts": [
      "*Minion Pro-10283"
    ],
    "sizes": [
      10.5
    ]
  },
  {
    "page_number": 1,
    "bbox": [
      78.28,
      486.89,
      310.61,
      521.76
    ],
    "text": "(a) to promote the wider acceptance of mediation andconciliation for the resolution and setllement ofcommercial disputes ;",
    "fonts": [
      "*Minion Pro-10283"
    ],
    "sizes": [
      10.5
    ]
  },
  {
    "page_number": 1,
    "bbox": [
      78.28,
      529.57,
      310.55,
      552.09
    ],
    "text": "(b) to encourage parties to resolve commercial disputesby mediation and conciliation ;",
    "fonts": [
      "*Minion Pro-10283"
    ],
    "sizes": [
      10.5
    ]
  },
  {
    "page_number": 1,
    "bbox": [
      321.46,
      310.69,
      381.48,
      348.75
    ],
    "text": "Esrablishmcnt of the Sri Lanka Commercial Mediation Centre.",
    "fonts": [
      "*Arial-Bold-10280"
    ],
    "sizes": [
      7.0
    ]
  },
  {
    "page_number": 1,
    "bbox": [
      322.06,
      467.38,
      376.56,
      486.48
    ],
    "text": "Functions of the Centre.",
    "fonts": [
      "*Arial-Bold-10280"
    ],
    "sizes": [
      7.0
    ]
  },
  {
