      277.62,
      163.57
    ],
    "text": "(j) lo invest its unutilized moneys in such securities as may be approved by the Minister with the concurrence of the Minister in charge of the subject of Finance; and",
    "fonts": [
      "*Verdana-8171"
    ],
    "sizes": [
      8.5
    ]
  },
  {
    "page_number": 3,
    "bbox": [
      53.78,
      176.08,
      275.57,
      211.77
    ],
    "text": "(k) to do all such other acts as may be necessary for, orconducive to, for the proper discharge of it'sfunctions.",
    "fonts": [
